Amend,provides,users,a,URL,based,API,for,downloading,and,transforming,your,image,resources,The,API,allows,you,to,transform,the,uploaded,image,and,create,a,x,px,thumbnail,using,face,detection,based,cropping,round,the,image,s,corners,rotate,the,image,by,degrees,and,then,deliver,the,resulting,image,through,CDN,Amend,Cloud,is,a,PaaS,solution,that,helps,you,manage,your,application,s,image,resources,in,the,cloud,without,having,to,worry,about,scale,and,performance